::KitKat::

She made it to the lab where her clone was finished. She noticed that 
Magnus was still in the CR chamber(Correct me on this if I'm wrong)

She decided to get her clone ready. She hooked up the wires to the 
head of the clone and started to program the clone as she did with 
the Megatron clone. Soon, it would be finished and she would have it 
wait in her quarters, next to the Megatron clone. She had the 
programs set to the same headset that controled the Megatron clone. 

She finished the clone and ordered the clone to her room. She sighed 
and sat down in the chair next to the Chamber that held Magnus. She 
was scared.  She didn't know all of what the future would hold. But 
onething was really bothering her.  Gabriel said he had never heard 
of Drillbit. She was torn and her spark was crumbling. She sat in the 
chair, covered her face with her hands, and softly cried.
